Governor Aminu Bello Masari of Katsina State, on Wednesday, said that the gunmen who attacked Government Science Secondary School in Kankara Local Government Area of the state and kidnapped schoolboys have been contacted. He added that the government was negotiating the boys’ freedom through the Miyetti Allah Cattle Breeders Association of Nigeria (MACBAN). Governor Aminu Masari Gunmen had on December 11 invaded the school, shooting into the air to scare away people in the area. As of December 13, Masari said over 300 students were confirmed missing. See Also






